          </div>
          <div class="p-6 flex-1 flex flex-col">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Project 2</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4 flex-1">
              Description of another impressive project. Be sure to highlight your role and the impact of the work.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
              <span class="bg-yellow-100 dark:bg-yellow-900 text-yellow-800 dark:text-yellow-100 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Vue.js</span>
              <span class="bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-900 text-red-800 dark:text-red-100 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Firebase</span>
              <span class="bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900 text-indigo-800 dark:text-indigo-100 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Tailwind</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mt-auto">
              <a href="#" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 dark:text-primary-400 dark:hover:text-primary-300 font-medium flex items-center gap-1 transition-colors">
                View Project 
